		{"id":"3c67232aa88027ad","x":-2005,"y":512,"width":673,"height":241,"type":"text","text":"**乌尔** 和 **哈兰** 都是**月神辛**（南纳）的主要场所。\n> The two chief seats of his worship were [Ur](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ur \"Ur\") in the south of Mesopotamia and [Harran](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Harran \"Harran\") in the north\n> - refs: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sin_%28mythology%29\n\n- Haran 位于土耳其、叙利亚边界，沿幼发拉底河 Euphrates River支流 Balikh River 以北 10 miles。在 Nuzi 石板总记载，月神辛在这里供奉。"},
		{"id":"ff4d151a4f460a83","x":-2005,"y":753,"width":673,"height":448,"color":"6","type":"text","text":"## 乌尔争议\nHaran 不远有两个城市：Ura and **Urfa**。\n- 当地传说亚伯拉罕出生于 **Urfa** （现 Şanlıurfa）\n- 亚伯拉罕派他的仆人回到哈兰地区，为以撒找妻子\n\t- 创 24:4 你要往我**本 地 本 族**去 ， 为我的儿子以撒娶一个妻子 。\n\t- 创 24:10 那仆人从他主人的骆驼里取了十匹骆驼，并带些他主人各样的财物，起身往米所波大米去，到了**拿 鹤**的城 。\n\t- He didn’t go to Sumer to find Isaac a wife, he went to Aram. Also see [Joshua 24:2–3](https://biblia.com/bible/esv/Josh%2024.2%E2%80%933).\n\t- 创 31:20 雅各背着亚兰人拉班偷走了，并不告诉他，就带着所有的逃跑。他起身**过大河**，面向基列山行去。\n\n\n\n> https://ready4eternity.com/which-ur-is-abrahams-ur/\n> http://www.accuracyingenesis.com/ur.html"},
